## ğŸ§  Environment Variables

| Variable      | Description              | Example      |
|---------------|--------------------------|--------------|
| `BLURT_MUTE`  | Mute all output          | `true`       |
| `BLURT_CONFIG`| JSON config for Blurt    | '{"rate": 180, "voice": "Alex"}' |

